 see what I will do to Pharaoh: for with a strong hand shall he let them go, and with a strong hand shall he drive them out of his land.","year":-1491},{"id":"recDWIqWyfIMCXWmU","ref":"Exod.6.2","text":"And God spake unto Moses, and said unto him, I am the LORD:","year":-1491},{"id":"recX7E5Yz7fl7bLRc","ref":"Exod.6.3","text":"And I appeared unto Abraham, unto Isaac, and unto Jacob, by the name of God Almighty, but by my name JEHOVAH was I not known to them.","year":-1491},{"id":"recmCcMNHILXgcKGn","ref":"Exod.6.4","text":"And I have also established my covenant with them, to give them the land of Canaan, the land of their pilgrimage, wherein they were strangers.","year":-1491},{"id":"recAfopvaJ2rGFszy","ref":"Exod.6.5","text":"And I have also heard the groaning of the children of Israel, whom the Egyptians keep in bondage; and I have remembered my covenant.","year":-1491},{"id":"recGTNJt9d47FERBr","ref":"Exod.6.6","text":"Wherefore say unto the children of Israel, I am the LORD, and I will bring you out from under the burdens of the Egyptians, and I will rid you out of their bondage, and I will redeem you with a stretched out arm, and with great judgments:","year":-1491},{"id":"recPyZczGHyjYdFBQ","ref":"Exod.6.7","text":"And I will take you to me for a people, and I will be to you a God: and ye shall know that I am the LORD your God, which bringeth you out from under the burdens of the Egyptians.","year":-1491},{"id":"recnU5O25pWd2nJcE","ref":"Exod.6.8","text":"And I will bring you in unto the land, concerning the which I did swear to give it to Abraham, to Isaac, and to Jacob; and I will give it you for an heritage: I am the LORD.","year":-1491}]}
